    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a standard action, you can assume the form of a Small fire elemental, as @Compendium[pf1.spells.pawbnw1nm4f0b98e]{Elemental Body I}.</p>\n<p>At 9th level, you can assume the form of a Medium fire elemental, as @Compendium[pf1.spells.yldjnorgbx4jsldz]{Elemental Body II}.</p>\n<p>At 11th level, you can assume the form of a Large fire elemental, as @Compendium[pf1.spells.hd32fuc6e7j4isbn]{Elemental Body III}.</p>\n<p>At 13th level, you can assume the form of a Huge fire elemental, as @Compendium[pf1.spells.v42t5kpxc8mvd615]{Elemental Body IV}.</p>\n<p>You can use this ability once per day, but the duration is 1 hour/level.</p>\n<p>You must be at least 7th level to select this revelation.</p>",
